    <main>
        <p><strong>AKDroid Labs
</strong> ("we," "our," or "us") operates the <strong>AuraLog: Mood & Energy Tracker</strong> mobile application (the "Service"). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service.</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3>A. Local Data (Mood & Energy Logs)</h3>
        <p>AuraLog is designed with a "Privacy First" philosophy. Your personal mood entries, energy logs, and "Aura Farming" data are stored locally on your device using a Room database.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>No Transmission:</strong> This data is not uploaded to our servers or shared with us.</li>
            <li><strong>User Control:</strong> You can delete this data at any time by clearing the app cache or uninstalling the application.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>B. Automated Data Collection (Third-Party Services)</h3>
        <p>To provide and maintain our Service, we use third-party tools that may collect information used to identify you:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Google AdMob:</strong> Our app displays advertisements. AdMob may collect your Advertising ID, IP address, and interaction data (e.g., ad clicks) to deliver personalized ads and prevent fraud.</li>
            <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> In the event of an app error, we may collect technical data (via third-party products) such as your device name, OS version, and the time of the error.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide and improve the Service.</li>
            <li><strong>Personalized Advertising:</strong> To show ads that are relevant to your interests.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> To understand user interaction and improve the app design.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p><strong>Encryption:</strong> All data transmitted to our third-party partners (like AdMob) is encrypted in transit using HTTPS/TLS protocols.</p>
        <p><strong>Security Disclaimer:</strong> While we use commercially acceptable means to protect your information, no method of electronic storage or transmission is 100% secure.</p>

        <h2>4. Your Privacy Rights and Choices</h2>
        <h3>A. Advertising ID Control</h3>
        <p>You can reset or opt-out of personalized ads through your Android device settings:</p>
        <p><em>Settings > Google > Ads > Reset/Delete Advertising ID.</em></p>
        
        <h3>B. Data Deletion</h3>
        <p>Since your mood data is stored locally, you have total control. Deleting the app will permanently remove all locally stored "Aura" data.</p>

        <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our Service is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we discover a child under 13 has provided us with personal data, we will delete it immediately.</p>

        <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>

        <div class="contact-box">
            <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
